---
description: Testing, quality and CI
alwaysApply: true
---

# Testing
- Cover domain logic and critical components.
- UI Testing: use Testing Library + Jest/Vitest.
- Naming: `*.test.ts[x]`.
- Test descriptions must be written in English.
- Every test case title must start with `should`.

# Quality
- Husky + lint-staged to block commits with lint/format errors.
- Run type-check and tests in CI.

# Delivery
- Descriptive commits (conventional if possible).
- Short and focused PRs, with impact checklist (UI, route, contract).
